---
title: Quick Mediterranean Honey Chicken with Israeli Couscous & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Who doesn’t love the signature combo of honey and succulent chicken. With tender pearls of Israeli couscous to soak
up all the flavour and a herby hit of dill-parsley mayonnaise, it'll make for a meal that you won’t be able to resist!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-mediterranean-honey-chicken-bowl-0ab7492b.jpg
